import sys

def main():
    n, t = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
    min_cost = t + 1
    for _ in range(n):
        cost, time = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())
        if time <= t:
            min_cost = min(min_cost, cost)
    if min_cost > t:
        print('TLE')
    else:
        print(min_cost)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
